description: Table 1 from the paper showing exposure parameters of CC-96673 following administration of single and first intravenous doses to cynomolgus monkeys in pharmacokinetic/toxicology studies.
footnotes: AUCLST = area under the concentration–time curve calculated to the last observable concentration at time t; CL = clearance; Cmax = observed maximum concentration; hr = hour; IV = intravenous; RD = repeat dose; SD = standard deviation; t½ = half-life; Vd = volume of distribution.
